    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/8129c60eff4c2ebd4252923186dca5ee.poster.avif?t=1767082798\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/8129c60eff4c2ebd4252923186dca5ee.webm?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/8129c60eff4c2ebd4252923186dca5ee.mp4?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After countless nightmares about your missing little sister, you embark on a journey with one goal: to bring her home. You play as Harley, a girl who’s going to face horrors worse than anything her nightmares could produce. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/10be13d539c2b5212029c694520fadc3.poster.avif?t=1767082798\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/10be13d539c2b5212029c694520fadc3.webm?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/10be13d539c2b5212029c694520fadc3.mp4?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/7c1d9e683f8668196c06f13d0ed14489.poster.avif?t=1767082798\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/7c1d9e683f8668196c06f13d0ed14489.webm?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/7c1d9e683f8668196c06f13d0ed14489.mp4?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-styled graphics reminiscent of the PS1 era! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic survival horror gameplay! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An atmospheric theme park with engaging puzzles! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory and storage box management!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice acted cutscenes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect (in-game) patches and outfits for achievements!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/c58053cc707df943534e5a2ef7da518b.poster.avif?t=1767082798\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/c58053cc707df943534e5a2ef7da518b.webm?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304730/extras/c58053cc707df943534e5a2ef7da518b.mp4?t=1767082798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
